---
import Button from "./Button.astro";
---

<section
  id="granting"
  class="bg-plum-darkest text-cream py-20 md:py-24"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-8">The granting process</h2>
    <div
      class="max-w-3xl space-y-5 font-sans text-base text-cream/80 leading-relaxed mb-10"
    >
      <p>
        We're building a new way to fund quantum biology… one that's
        community-driven, transparent, and designed to support experiments that
        matter.
      </p>
      <p>
        Right now, the full granting process is still in development. But if
        you're interested in connecting or have any ideas:
      </p>
    </div>
    <Button
      href="https://quantumbiology.community"
      variant="primary"
      size="md"
      external>Visit our Discord</Button
    >
  </div>
</section>
